    <title>Hexo安装与基础设置</title>
    <url>/2021/10/12/Hexo%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="0-git服务相关设置"><a href="#0-git服务相关设置" class="headerlink" title="0. git服务相关设置"></a>0. git服务相关设置</h1><ol>
<li><p>创建用于存放Hexo工程项目的git仓库，任意仓库即可，用于存储Hexo的配置和原始博客文件</p>
</li>
<li><p>创建git服务的<code>ssh公钥</code>并设置，用于发布Hexo博客</p>
</li>
<li><p>创建用于Hexo的发布仓库，用于Hexo生成静态网页后发布并对位访问</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Git服务</th>
<th>指定仓库名</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>github</td>
<td>&lt;username&gt;.github.io</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="1-安装Hexo"><a href="#1-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装Hexo"></a>1. 安装Hexo</h1><h2 id="1-1-初始化一些环境"><a href="#1-1-初始化一些环境" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 初始化一些环境"></a>1.1. 初始化一些环境</h2><ol>
<li><p>安装<code>node.js</code>，并写入全局变量</p>
</li>
<li><p>安装<code>Hexo</code></p>
 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>初始化Hexo基础工程文件到指定目录，该目录可以同步至git进行版本管理</p>
 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;hexo_dir&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="1-2-初步使用"><a href="#1-2-初步使用" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 初步使用"></a>1.2. 初步使用</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &lt;blog_title&gt;	<span class="comment"># 新建新blog文件，并初始化文件头部</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g		<span class="comment"># 生成静态网页文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s		<span class="comment"># 启动本地服务器，默认为 http://localhost:4000</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean	<span class="comment"># 清理生成的文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="1-3-推送静态网站"><a href="#1-3-推送静态网站" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 推送静态网站"></a>1.3. 推送静态网站</h2><ol>
<li><p>在<code>Hexo</code>的根目录下找到文件<code>_config.yml</code>，并修改如下配置</p>
 <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span> <span class="comment"># 发布</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&lt;git服务&gt;:</span> <span class="string">&lt;仓库SSH连接&gt;,</span> <span class="string">&lt;分支&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">gitbub:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:&lt;username&gt;:&lt;username&gt;.github.io,</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><code>Hexo</code>安装<code>git</code>插件</p>
 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>推送生成的静态网页</p>
 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g	<span class="comment"># 产生文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d	<span class="comment"># 发布项目</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><code>_config.yml</code>其他一些配置修改</p>
 <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">KeeKalm</span> <span class="string">Note</span>	<span class="comment"># 站点名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">KeeKalm</span>	<span class="comment"># 作者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span>	<span class="comment"># 语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">Asia/Shanghai</span>	<span class="comment"># 时区</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Set your site url here. For example, if you use GitHub Page, set url as &#x27;https://username.github.io/project&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://keekalm.github.io/</span>	<span class="comment"># 站点URL</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
